OL,7,FA former "successful and accomplished
OL,8,Fsoldier" turned military clerk stole
OL,9,Fnearly #1 million from the Ministry of
OL,10,FDefence by creating fake expenses
OL,11,Fclaims.
OL,13,FFormer Corporal Aaron Stelmach-Purdie,
OL,14,F34, entered the false claims into the
OL,15,Fdepartment's online administrative
OL,16,Fsystem while he worked as a clerk at
OL,17,Fthe Ministry of Defence's
OL,18,Fadministrative headquarters in central
OL,19,FLondon.
