OL,3,CFormer 'successful and accomplished
OL,4,Csoldier' stole #1m from Ministry of
OL,5,CDefence
OL,7,FStelmach-Purdie, from Oldham, who ran
OL,8,Fthe scam between November 2014 and
OL,9,FJanuary 2016, manipulated the online
OL,10,Fplatform for the management of staff's
OL,11,Fexpenses and allowance claims,
OL,12,Fdefrauding the Government out of
OL,13,F#911,677 - keeping #557,093 for
OL,14,Fhimself.
OL,16,FHe was jailed for three years and four
OL,17,Fmonths after admitting fraud and money
OL,18,Flaundering.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
