OL,5,CDefence
OL,7,FStelmach-Purdie, who joined the Army
OL,8,Fat the age of 16 and served in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland and Afghanistan,
OL,10,Ftravelled to Turkey to purchase hair
OL,11,Ftransplants, teeth-whitening and
OL,12,Fabdominal implants with the money he
OL,13,Fstole, Southwark Crown Court
OL,14,Fpreviously heard.
OL,16,FPolice officers searched his home and
OL,17,Ffound a Louis Vuitton luggage set and
OL,18,Fnine pairs of Christian Louboutin
OL,19,Fshoes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
