OL,7,FFive other military clerks who were
OL,8,Falso employed at the Regent's Park
OL,9,FBarracks - former sergeant Roger
OL,10,FClerice, 28, Allan O'Neil, 48, Lee
OL,11,FRichards, 41, Anthony Sharwood, 38,
OL,12,Fand Peter Wilson, 55 - were sentenced
OL,13,Falongside Stelmach-Purdie after they
OL,14,Fwere convicted over charges of money
OL,15,Flaundering and conspiracy to commit
OL,16,Ffraud.
OL,18,FHis Honour Judge Philip Bartle KC said
OL,19,FStelmach-Purdie played a "leading role
OL,20,Fin the fraud" having previously been a
OL,21,F"successful and accomplished soldier".
