OL,7,FStelmach-Purdie used the bank accounts
OL,8,Fof others to hide the money and lied
OL,9,Fto his mother, sister and a friend,
OL,10,FSimon Lees, as to where the funds had
OL,11,Fcome from, the court heard.
OL,13,FAfter an investigation was launched,
OL,14,FStelmach-Purdie said in interview that
OL,15,Fhe became "aware that people were
OL,16,Fmaking claims for allowances that they
OL,17,Fwere not entitled to" after taking an
OL,18,Fadministration job following
OL,19,F"traumatising tours in Afghanistan".
