OL,7,FProsecutors said the fraud centred
OL,8,Faround the use of the Joint Personnel
OL,9,FAdministration (JPA) ` an online
OL,10,Fadministrative system used by the
OL,11,Farmed forces to pay the salaries of
OL,12,Fstaff and claims for expenses and
OL,13,Fallowances.
OL,15,FWhile responsible for the management
OL,16,Fof claims, Stelmach-Purdie made
OL,17,Ffraudulent claims on his JPA account
OL,18,Fand those of others for operational
OL,19,Fallowances, subsistence allowances and
OL,20,Fair fares.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
