OL,7,FThe other defendants told the court
OL,8,Fthey were approached by Stelmach-
OL,9,FPurdie in or shortly after December
OL,10,F2014, when he claimed he had found a
OL,11,Fway to "make some money manipulating
OL,12,FJPA".
OL,14,FWilson, a former lance sergeant who
OL,15,Fretired from the Army in October 2015,
OL,16,Fhad #378,662.26 pass through his bank
OL,17,Faccount from Stelmach-Purdie, of which
OL,18,Fhe retained #149,781.
