OL,14,FWilson has the muscle-wasting
OL,15,FCharcot`Marie`Tooth disease and has
OL,16,Fbeen invited to trials by the Great
OL,17,FBritain paralympic rowing team for the
OL,18,Fnext Games in Los Angeles.
