OL,7,FRichards, a former lance sergeant from
OL,8,FAmesbury in Wiltshire, was convicted
OL,9,Fby a jury of more than 100 fraudulent
OL,10,Fclaims made between March 2015 and
OL,11,FJanuary 2016, involving #434,825.
OL,13,FHe retained approximately #160,000 of
OL,14,Fthat sum, the court heard.
OL,16,FStelmach-Purdie initially approached
OL,17,FRichards, who worked at the barracks
OL,18,Fas a storeman, by telling him he was
OL,19,F"under a lot of pressure" and needed
OL,20,Fto book flights, the court heard.
